1047
01:20:30,960 --> 01:20:33,320
I'm honored by your presence.

1048
01:20:36,920 --> 01:20:37,920
- Majesty?
- Yes.

1049
01:20:40,760 --> 01:20:44,280
I know the person
you had arrested.

1050
01:20:44,520 --> 01:20:45,720
I know...

1051
01:20:45,920 --> 01:20:48,400
and I know you care for him.

1052
01:20:49,680 --> 01:20:51,360
He's an exceptional person.

1053
01:20:51,800 --> 01:20:55,160
- He lost his son in...
