1165
01:30:26,680 --> 01:30:30,560
who knows how much longer
I'll have to tell you this...

1166
01:30:33,480 --> 01:30:35,720
I allowed myself to be conquered
by the Emperor...

1167
01:30:35,920 --> 01:30:38,840
